QUESTION:

Write a program to find whether the given number is positive or negative.

Input & Output Format:

Input consists of a integer.

if it is positive display "Positive" or else display "Negative 

if it is zero display "Equal to 0"

Sample Input:

2

Sample Output:

Positive

CODING:

#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    int num;
    cin>>num;
    if(num>0)
    {
        cout<<" Positive";
    }
    else if(num==0)
    {
      cout<<"Equal to 0";
    }
    else 
    {
      cout<<"Negative";
    }
}    
